/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock
# ...but DO commit the native crate's lock: the `native` CI lane builds it as a
# verified artifact, so it must resolve the exact deps (pyo3 patch) it was
# verified against, not float on every CI run.
!native/Cargo.lock
*.so
*.dylib
*.dll
*.pdb
.env
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
